"title": "8352: thankfulness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8352",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Heartfelt gratitude to God, expressed in response to his love and mercy.</p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for God's goodness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4-Ps100:5\">PSA 100:4–100:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:8\">1CH 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:34-1Chr16:35\">1CH 16:34–16:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:3-2Chr7:6\">2CH 7:3–7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10-Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:19\">PSA 68:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:1\">PSA 106:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:12-Ps116:14\">PSA 116:12–116:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:1-Ps136:3\">PSA 136:1–136:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:26\">PSA 136:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for deliverance</h2>\n<h3>From adversity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:9-Ps35:10\">PSA 35:9–35:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:7-Ps31:8\">PSA 31:7–31:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:21-Ps31:23\">PSA 31:21–31:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:6-Ps44:8\">PSA 44:6–44:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:8-Ps66:9\">PSA 66:8–66:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:16-Ps66:20\">PSA 66:16–66:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:1-Ps103:5\">PSA 103:1–103:5</a></p>\n<h3>From slavery in Egypt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20-Exod15:21\">EXO 15:20–15:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:1-Exod15:18\">EXO 15:1–15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:1-Ps105:45\">PSA 105:1–105:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:1-Ps136:26\">PSA 136:1–136:26</a></p>\n<h3>From the power of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:53-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:53–15:57</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for answered prayer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1-1Sam2:10\">1SA 2:1–2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:1-Ps30:12\">PSA 30:1–30:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:16-Ps66:20\">PSA 66:16–66:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:1-Ps138:5\">PSA 138:1–138:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:40\">JHN 11:40</a></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:4\">PHM 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:17\">NEH 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:8\">ROM 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2\">COL 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1\">1TI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:3\">2TI 1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:32\">LUK 2:25–2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:36-Luke2:38\">LUK 2:36–2:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:6\">COL 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15-Col3:17\">COL 3:15–3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Thankfulness for God's provision</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:19\">MAT 14:19</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:41\">MRK 6:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:16\">LUK 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:11\">JHN 6:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:7-Ps147:9\">PSA 147:7–147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:36\">MAT 15:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:6\">MRK 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:26-Matt26:27\">MAT 26:26–26:27</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:22-Mark14:23\">MRK 14:22–14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:17-Luke22:19\">LUK 22:17–22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:30\">LUK 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:35\">ACT 27:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:6\">ROM 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:3\">1TI 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Means of expressing thankfulness to God</h2>\n<h3>In song</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:19-Eph5:20\">EPH 5:19–5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30\">PSA 69:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:2\">PSA 95:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:1\">PSA 96:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:12\">ISA 55:12</a></p>\n<h3>In music</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:6\">PSA 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:1-Ps92:3\">PSA 92:1–92:3</a></p>\n<h3>In dance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:3\">PSA 149:3</a></p>\n<h3>In worship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:2\">PSA 95:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:28\">HEB 12:28</a></p>",
